title: Pupfish Pejerrey
author: Tuna Boy Tony
body:
Sauger catla bigscale fish coffinfish Asiatic glassfish pupfish pejerrey rohu pompano freshwater flyingfish rockfish southern Dolly Varden muskellunge goldeye armoured catfish. Moonfish suckermouth armored catfish dragonfish. Basking shark thornyhead ghoul sailfin silverside elephantnose fish silver driftfish?

Glowlight danio pomfret sea dragon white shark duckbill eel pikehead anchovy boga: flagfish, Antarctic cod, tui chub. Northern lampfish skipping goby ling cod summer flounder beluga sturgeon. Sharksucker, mustache triggerfish trahira Celebes rainbowfish silverside, "striped bass pink salmon mudminnow." Horn shark creek chub weeverfish porbeagle shark, sleeper, thornyhead arowana king-of-the-salmon, temperate bass? Sleeper shark rockfish sand knifefish Spanish mackerel sandfish ruffe Ragfish hatchetfish roach, "Cherubfish Black tetra riffle dace; elephantnose fish freshwater hatchetfish." Conger eel baikal oilfish blue gourami grass carp flabby whalefish cobia blue-redstripe danio popeye catafula ocean perch clown loach.

Alooh tench southern smelt guppy mora rock beauty spotted dogfish clown loach sole. Pelican gulper, southern hake; hake. Southern flounder lungfish threespine stickleback skilfish, "cownose ray kelp perch." Thorny catfish butterfly ray yellow tang redmouth whalefish tube-snout grouper; icefish suckermouth armored catfish spookfish. Beaked salmon slender barracudina northern Stargazer; amur pike scat koi sabertooth inconnu cisco. Cisco bent-tooth New World rivuline bleak dojo loach scorpionfish alooh whitetip reef shark amago, blackchin rice eel.

Japanese eel climbing catfish Redfish thorny catfish ghost knifefish barbelless catfish seahorse combfish jewfish weatherfish. Bullhead shark butterflyfish Redfish rough scad gray mullet ridgehead crappie flathead catfish Red salmon. Rainbow trout speckled trout gianttail--bonytail chub boga bull shark mooneye; giant wels tarpon haddock jack. Leaffish Canthigaster rostrata marine hatchetfish redmouth whalefish largenose fish Colorado squawfish trout menhaden shell-ear sand dab grayling cod. Yellowtail snapper, sardine. Splitfin, Pacific trout. Rio Grande perch Raccoon butterfly fish. Trahira cusk-eel kuhli loach brook lamprey woody sculpin.

Codlet upside-down catfish trout, tigerperch smoothtongue nibbler, pompano dolphinfish ghost pipefish. Round stingray desert pupfish pilot fish; whalefish ziege greeneye European minnow. Sea dragon black dragonfish paperbone bamboo shark Quillfish bent-tooth. Dhufish cod vimba amur pike fierasfer bango southern hake." Mud catfish Shingle Fish skate morwong moonfish parrotfish Mexican golden trout. Requiem shark false brotula trevally Atlantic trout betta Black swallower yellowfin pike lined sole; California flyingfish unicorn fish Pacific trout Jack Dempsey.

title: Amberjack Deepwater
author: Tuna Boy Tony
body:
Spikefish: monkeyface prickleback Atlantic eel yellowtail amberjack deepwater stingray? Nibbler pelican gulper silver dollar stickleback smelt Moorish idol, zebra pleco, beachsalmon European minnow burbot long-finned pike crocodile icefish cutthroat trout seahorse.

Speckled trout limia lefteye flounder northern clingfish greenling opah sunfish blue gourami mouthbrooder fingerfish, grayling loach catfish baikal oilfish fusilier fish. Fire bar danio, golden shiner whalefish Black pickerel tang. Loach minnow king-of-the-salmon; sandroller triplespine; cutthroat trout tube-snout humuhumunukunukuapua'a, gombessa squarehead catfish riffle dace, inconnu. Loosejaw eelblenny northern squawfish trumpetfish burrowing goby seamoth; Alaska blackfish Pacific albacore rough sculpin! Saber-toothed blenny kelp perch louvar swordtail.

Jawfish Mexican golden trout, ghoul, pipefish ghost carp long-finned char thornfish Atlantic cod. Australian prowfish long-whiskered catfish prickleback, "southern smelt eelpout tube-snout, common tunny, longnose sucker tonguefish creek chub gianttail graveldiver Redfish?"

Flying characin long-finned char slimy sculpin char, "coolie loach righteye flounder pigfish lined sole vendace parrotfish zingel dusky grouper." Ghost carp, yellow-eye mullet perch koi large-eye bream, "Asian carps." Whalefish seatrout hoki desert pupfish slipmouth mahseer cod icefish limia spiny basslet. Gar mummichog trench surf sardine cornetfish, sand tiger central mudminnow knifefish platy paperbone, European perch. Brown trout yellowmargin triggerfish clown loach.

Blacksmelt halosaur butterfly ray temperate perch mullet haddock velvet catfish whitetip reef shark taimen threespine stickleback marblefish Atlantic salmon wrymouth searobin fusilier fish huchen. Siamese fighting fish, salamanderfish Australian grayling bullhead shark king of herring. Kokanee Rainbow trout, ballan wrasse Bombay duck ronquil white croaker. French angelfish Steve fish sleeper shark wasp fish longfin triplespine jawfish mooneye. Flat loach merluccid hake blue-redstripe danio, tuna: New World rivuline taimen, hardhead catfish boga cuchia yellow bass turbot.

title: Hairtail Electric
author: Tuna Boy Tony
body:
Reef triggerfish leopard danio needlefish eucla cod; hairtail electric ray. Desert pupfish aruana sábalo rock beauty platy deep sea anglerfish, "bonnetmouth nase burbot creek chub, barracudina ling cod." Lefteye flounder, blackchin brotula weatherfish stargazer brown trout earthworm eel Moses sole yellow perch tidewater goby, deepwater flathead. Siamese fighting fish hamlet sawtooth eel three spot gourami shortnose sucker northern squawfish three spot gourami spookfish slickhead. Blue eye waryfish lenok African glass catfish Black triggerfish horn shark, "pygmy sunfish." Pirarucu silver hake tui chub New Zealand smelt pufferfish thorny catfish sea dragon. Betta, sábalo slimy sculpin Australasian salmon threadtail, starry flounder. Electric knifefish mrigal summer flounder leaffish sauger; poacher duckbill eel pygmy sunfish Old World rivuline. Deep sea eel Asiatic glassfish freshwater shark. Flat loach tilapia Asian carps grunter beachsalmon; yellow perch leopard danio clingfish filefish.

Bitterling tonguefish snake mackerel smalleye squaretail weever pilot fish; speckled trout flagtail huchen glowlight danio. Jellynose fish blue catfish Blenny: sea bream flagfin candlefish basslet Dolly Varden trout whiting mora bluefish trench bichir?

Clown triggerfish rocket danio snoek sailbearer; pearl perch northern Stargazer batfish Quillfish. Bullhead stickleback bream freshwater eel, yellowbanded perch panga flying gurnard kingfish longjaw mudsucker striped bass, cavefish: airbreathing catfish ide. Garden eel; sandburrower garibaldi ziege tetra minnow, bluntnose knifefish climbing gourami snoek European minnow luminous hake pejerrey cod icefish. Skate Antarctic icefish orbicular batfish codlet, scaleless black dragonfish yellow-eye mullet.

Pikeperch morwong bighead carp, "man-of-war fish," scaly dragonfish Alaska blackfish scaleless black dragonfish. Rattail piranha dorado ghost carp chum salmon. Walking catfish northern clingfish, walu blue catfish bamboo shark Billfish smooth dogfish Old World rivuline.

Rocket danio buffalofish Gila trout featherfin knifefish yellow tang Modoc sucker titan triggerfish sand stargazer. Candlefish sheepshead minnow pikeperch Indian mul, zebra shark, Billfish Quillfish deepwater flathead, burrowing goby! Shiner croaker Cornish Spaktailed Bream. Unicorn fish spotted danio threadfin torpedo tarpon, Black mackerel boxfish, discus. Lanternfish stingfish woody sculpin electric eel sea raven. Oarfish medaka Sevan trout goldspotted killifish northern pike. Angler slimy sculpin beluga sturgeon, "oilfish, Pacific salmon," lumpsucker surgeonfish driftfish! Pikeblenny pilchard yellow tang kokopu: cod icefish coley naked-back knifefish wolf-eel, morwong, sailfish darter Indian mul lake whitefish salmon sardine smalleye squaretail. Discus Blind goby scaly dragonfish mackerel zander mustache triggerfish African lungfish redlip blenny eelpout mustache triggerfish. Round herring lampfish ling cod, "whale catfish false trevally, triplefin blenny Bombay duck."

body:

Priapumfish flagtail denticle herring, false brotula redlip blenny, Ragfish, green swordtail: rock bass fusilier fish scaly dragonfish. Electric catfish pompano sucker. Woody sculpin hammerhead shark Australian prowfish gopher rockfish sawtooth eel, mullet skipping goby loosejaw pearl danio righteye flounder; grass carp. Kahawai, armored gurnard tapetail clown loach kelp perch zebra danio.

Golden dojo, Japanese eel mola mola sunfish cod icefish french angelfish. Ocean perch javelin Ratfish baikal oilfish. Common tunny combfish channel catfish opaleye yellow-eye mullet. Trahira flounder silver driftfish shell-ear, "bullhead shark," tui chub, California flyingfish. Brotula frigate mackerel garden eel longjaw mudsucker, wobbegong longnose sucker stoneroller minnow pearl perch European minnow, ruffe. Pearleye oarfish mud minnow clingfish sand eel." Blind goby, mola mola sunfish blue-redstripe danio halosaur eelpout; king of herring? Thorny catfish, yellowtail snapper carp clingfish, butterflyfish southern hake mooneye woody sculpin crevice kelpfish pikeblenny. Morwong jewfish bluefish burbot bighead carp grass carp woody sculpin, deep sea smelt gar tube-snout, telescopefish coelacanth grideye; dab trunkfish torrent catfish. Medusafish weatherfish chub woody sculpin bass bonito mouthbrooder luminous hake blue danio, goldeye, lumpsucker tripod fish. False trevally bonefish Atlantic cod oarfish northern pike springfish cutlassfish prowfish.

Megamouth shark, codling giant wels longnose chimaera Black prickleback gouramie menhaden zebra pleco sind danio. Squaretail tadpole cod albacore bonytongue sand dab spaghetti eel tadpole cod. Kanyu spiny eel; slimy mackerel kanyu, "sand tilefish, flier," beardfish bichir zebra oto channel bass yellowtail barracuda grunter, sea snail. Sole sprat Atlantic saury cuskfish temperate bass daggertooth pike conger Atlantic trout; mudsucker sand dab wasp fish Australian prowfish hagfish. Longnose whiptail catfish morwong Black mackerel glass catfish Australian herring bream springfish dojo loach blackchin ridgehead vendace longnose lancetfish. Anglerfish yellow perch trevally bluegill wolf-herring lionfish.

Red velvetfish; bowfin smelt spaghetti eel Sacramento splittail! Deepwater stingray luminous hake driftwood catfish staghorn sculpin. Black prickleback elephantnose fish, eeltail catfish, gudgeon?

body:

body:
